with the whereabouts of a 15-year-old girl who disappeared last week.Musetsho Anzani, a pupil at Mbilwi High School in
Makwarela Extension 03, was last seen by
her mother leaving home for school to write her examinations on Friday and she
never returned home.Police spokesperson Colonel Moatshe Ngoepe, said she is
